ZH: 这个水果需要先冲洗，然后才能吃。
EN: This fruit needs to be washed before it can be eaten.

ZH: 我每天都会用清水冲洗蔬菜。
EN: I wash my vegetables with clean water every day.

ZH: 请把这些衣服放进洗衣机冲洗。
EN: Please put these clothes in the washing machine to wash.

ZH: 水龙头坏了，无法用来冲洗。
EN: The faucet is broken and can't be used for washing.

ZH: 这个碗需要仔细冲洗才能很干净。
EN: This bowl needs to be thoroughly washed to be clean.

ZH: 老师让我们用漂白水冲洗实验器材。
EN: The teacher asked us to wash the lab equipment with bleach.

ZH: 他用高压喷水器冲洗了车子。
EN: He washed the car with a high-pressure water sprayer.

ZH: 请记得在冲洗后把水龙头关上。
EN: Please remember to turn off the faucet after washing.

ZH: 这个杯子已经冲洗过了，可以用来喝水。
EN: This cup has been washed and can be used for drinking water.

ZH: 妈妈正在厨房冲洗碗碟。
EN: Mom is washing the dishes in the kitchen.

ZH: 喷雾器可以用来冲洗草地。
EN: The sprayer can be used to wash the lawn.

ZH: 这块肉需要先冲洗，然后再下锅烹饪。
EN: This piece of meat needs to be washed before cooking.

ZH: 冲洗头发的时候要用温水。
EN: Use warm water when washing your hair.

ZH: 不要直接用肥皂冲洗蔬菜，会留下化学物质。
EN: Don't wash vegetables directly with soap, it will leave chemical residue.

ZH: 运动服需要用专门的洗涤剂冲洗。
EN: Sports clothing needs to be washed with special detergent.

ZH: 这种鱼需要冲洗并去鳞才能煮。
EN: This fish needs to be washed and scaled before cooking.

ZH: 请确保把新衣服冲洗干净再穿。
EN: Please make sure to wash new clothes before wearing them.

ZH: 工人正在用高压水枪冲洗地面。
EN: Workers are using high-pressure water guns to wash the floor.

ZH: 冲洗感觉清新又舒适。
EN: Washing makes you feel fresh and comfortable.
